WEBVTT

00:02.170 --> 00:04.263
Dembe, I trust Raymond.
I do.

00:04.330 --> 00:08.699
He and I go back decades.
But what the hell is going on?

00:08.770 --> 00:12.228
I wake up this morning,
make an espresso,
open the paper...

00:14.480 --> 00:15.538
It's under control.

00:15.610 --> 00:17.498
We have hundreds
of millions of dollars

00:17.580 --> 00:18.899
invested in Reddington.

00:18.980 --> 00:22.211
Which have always returned
a handsome profit.

00:22.290 --> 00:25.418
Your boss is looking
at the death penalty.

00:25.490 --> 00:27.549
What happens
if he cuts a deal?

00:27.620 --> 00:30.259
Do you believe that Raymond
would cut a deal with the FBI?

00:32.030 --> 00:33.793
My partners do.

00:33.860 --> 00:36.590
Carlo Androssani
thinks we should
cut ties with Reddington,

00:36.670 --> 00:39.662
insulate ourselves from
any of the, uh, fallout.

00:40.500 --> 00:41.535
Is that a threat?

00:41.600 --> 00:42.806
He called for a vote.

00:42.870 --> 00:45.100
Can Raymond count
on your support?

00:45.170 --> 00:46.706
I'm the least
of his problems.

00:46.780 --> 00:48.338
Does he have your vote?

00:50.850 --> 00:52.215
Yes.

00:53.050 --> 00:54.540
But you prepare for war.

00:54.620 --> 00:57.418
Carlo and the others
are out for blood.

00:57.490 --> 00:59.708
