far away*

01:37.030 --> 01:38.088
Cyn?

01:39.900 --> 01:44.189
Cyn? Oh, my God.
Cyn, can you hear me?

01:44.270 --> 01:47.330
Cynthi... Please, honey!
Open your eyes!

01:47.400 --> 01:48.662
