to recall prepositions

10:04.270 --> 10:06.022
is a common symptom
of aphasia.

10:06.100 --> 10:09.831
Recommended therapies include
word games, rote repetition,

10:09.910 --> 10:12.606
uh, either on your own
or in a individualized,

10:12.680 --> 10:15.171
one-on-one,
or group-therapy format.
Under. Above. Following.

10:15.240 --> 10:18.801
The important thing
is to start early.
To. Unto. Despite. Without.

