"Quetzals."

10:20.220 --> 10:21.972
That is the national bird
of Guatemala

10:22.050 --> 10:24.541
and, weirdly, one of
its monetary units.

10:24.620 --> 10:26.178
Good to know. _
No, waIt, wait, waIt, wait.

10:26.250 --> 10:28.059
No, no. If you put
the Q and the S
on the triple word score,

10:28.120 --> 10:29.382
